missionEventData.data2: In the far reaches of the Outer Rim a rebellion is forming. A rebel cell led by the frigate Redemption and ace pilot Keyan Farlander have been striking back against the evil galactic empire. But the Emperor is at the height of his power, and even now he is marshalling his forces at the edge of the mid-rim. But help has come from the most unlikely of places. The captain of an imperial corvette has sent the rebel freedom fighters a secret message, he wishes to defect...

missionEventData.data1: With the assistance of the Cygnus staff, the crew of the Ars Opus has escaped and jumped the system. We believe they're headed for an Imperial safe point. Get after them immediately, if they share our location or the plans we've been making our position in this sector will be lost.
Red Squadron head to the jump point immediately.
Ars Opus, this is your final warning, surrender or we will force our way on board the vessel.
Reinforce your shields, we need to take out those turrets before we can signal the boarding craft.
Detecting ship exiting Hyperspace. It's a lancer class frigate.
This is two. I'm detecting five tie fighters launching.
This is Ars Opus hailing Lancer Frigate Advantage. We're beaming across to you the position of the Rebel fleet.
Red 2 and 3. That Frigate can't leave the system. Arm torpedos and begin your run.
Space Turrets destroyed. Activating beacon for boarding craft.
This is DX9 Transport Gold One. Preparing to disable the Ars Opus.
The Ars Opus has been disabled.
My God... they blew her up...
There's nothing else to do here. Return to base.
Ars Opus you are not authorised for departure. Power down your engines and prepare for boarding.
I'm picking up a spike in their energy readings. Looks like they're about to jump.
R4 get a lock on their trajectory and calculate their most likely destination.
Red Squadron. I'm sending you the new jump coordinates. Get after them immediately.
